reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic Charging Cable for All My Devices!

Lightning-Fast Charging: As someone who relies heavily on their devices, fast charging is a must. These cables deliver on their promise of 3.1A fast charging, ensuring that my devices are juiced up quickly and efficiently. It's a game-changer, especially when I'm in a rush and need a quick power boost. Durable and Tangle-Free: These cables are not only durable but also tangle-resistant. I can toss them in my bag, and they come out without any annoying knots or kinks. This attention to detail really sets them apart. Sleek Black Design: The black color adds a touch of elegance to my charging setup. They blend in seamlessly with my devices and look great. Affordable 2-Pack: Getting two cables in one package at such an affordable price is a steal. It means I always have a backup cable on hand or can share one with a friend in need.In conclusion, the JSAUX USB-C to USB A Cable 3.1A Fast Charging [2-Pack 6.6ft] has exceeded my expectations in every way. It's a reliable, fast-charging solution that works with all my devices, and the build quality ensures it will stand the test of time. If you're in need of new charging cables, I wholeheartedly recommend these. You won't be disappointed!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks Better in Person!
reviews.reviewText: These are some of the nicest USB cables I've ever seen. The braiding is top quality, the cable ends are incredibly rugged, and the rubber for "strain relief" is at a nice length and a solid addition for a cable's longevity.I ordered the 10FT as I intended to use these with controllers for couch gaming. So far they fit and work with most standard controllers(Xbox Series X, Switch Pro Controller, PS5, etc.), however this cable did not fit my GameSir G7 SE controller BUT it did fit the GameSir T4 Kaleid(albeit VERY TIGHTLY). I am blaming the port design from GameSir for being too tight fitting, however this is a good reminder that even though things are moving to USB-C, it doesn't mean that all cables will fit all devices physically, so be careful!I will definitely buy more of these cables if I need more in the future.
